INSERT INTO action_text_rich_texts VALUES(68,'description',replace('<div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  The objective of this Project is to define which criteria a Lead should match in order to be able to schedule a Discovery Call (rather it''s direct or through a setter).\n\nIs it a certain threshold of Annual Revenue? Employee Count? \n\nShould we use BANT? If so, what would the thresholds for Budget, Authority, Needs and Timing be? \n\nIs it a combination of it all?\n\nOnce we have this figured out, the next step is to implement it in the forms (for Direct schedules), BDR scripts (for Setter schedules) and CRM to ensure there is consistent data for conversion tracking, etc\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','\n',char(10)),'Project',68,'2025-01-09 15:15:59.381878','2025-05-20 17:52:58.329967');
INSERT INTO action_text_rich_texts VALUES(80,'description',replace('<div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  The objective of this project is to provide as much information as possible about the quality of a client to AMs before the Welcome Call. In order to do that, we need to have a set of attributes that we''ll use to measure the quality of the client. \n\nThis is specially tricky when there are so many things that seem crucial for us to measure client quality. Is it industry? Traffic? Business maturity (both in revenue and in systems/tracking)?  \n\nWhile in the ideal world we''d like to sell only to the best clients, we know that that''s not possible - at least in the short term. But, if we can have an understanding of the quality of a client beforehand and allocate resources accordingly, that''s already an amazing optimization.\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','\n',char(10)),'Project',80,'2025-01-09 19:08:07.778110','2025-04-17 18:47:00.622123');
INSERT INTO action_text_rich_texts VALUES(82,'description',replace('<div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  <div class="trix-content">\n  Everything related to DCs generated by Paid Ads. Google Ads had worked quite well in the past, then we lost traction after moving ads management to NPA''s internal team and launching Meta Ads. Now, we''re back working with a vendor for Meta Ads with a Form Fill style of ads (before it was just direct booking calendar)\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','\n',char(10)),'Project',82,'2025-01-13 20:02:25.310227','2025-05-20 17:54:38.437440');
